		<description>&lt;color=#edad56&gt;This technique is learned by the Primordial spirit maturity rank of the Forge method\n\n&lt;/color&gt;Qi cost: 450\n\nWith their own spirit as the material, make a spiritual spirit with innate components, this raw material can be used as the core of a weapon armor and other items.</description>
